Package: open.meteo.com
Title: Open-Meteo Weather API Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for the Open-Meteo weather forecast and historical
    data API. Covers hourly forecasts, daily summaries, and historical archive.
    Includes LLM context injection via meteo_context().
